				Tally of Loan to Lender, and Warrant for Interest at £6 per Cent. per Ann. to be paid every Three Months. Persons furnishing the Navy and Ordnance to have Warrant for;
Payment on Certificate, which is to be had without Fee.; Orders for Re-payment to be registered according to Date of Tally, and paid in course; ; without Preference.;Whether for Payment of Moniei lent or for Goods, &c. furnished to the Navy, &c.; Monies to come in by this A&bholigct; liable to satisfy such Loans.; No Fee for providing or making Books, &c.; or for Payment of Money lent; Penalty.; Punishment. ; Undue Preference by Officer; Penalty.
